data.title: List of people from the Dominican Republic
data.text:
For a list of people from the Commonwealth of Dominica, see List of people from Dominica.

This is a list of famous or notable people from the Dominican Republic. The list also includes individuals of Dominican ancestry who reside overseas.

This is a dynamic list and may never be able to satisfy particular standards for completeness. You can help by adding missing items with reliable sources.
